data.description: Dreaming of Suburban Bliss? Dive into this All-Brick, 4 Bedroom Haven in Columbus, GA! Moments from Ft. Benning, this home marries elegance with comfort. Featuring a formal living and dining room, an eat-in kitchen overlooking a cozy den, and a private pool view. Indulge in luxury with rich hardwood floors and a master suite boasting a modern walk-in shower. Plus, a spacious backyard with deck and patio perfect for poolside gatherings. Don’t let this exquisite find slip away! Please call before viewing, do not disturb the occupants.
